POLICY NUMBER: COMMERCIAL AUTO
THIS ENDORSEMENT CHANGES THE POLICY. PLEASE READ IT CAREFULLY.
NON-OWNED OR HIRED AUTO ENDORSEMENT
This endorsement modifies insurance provided under the following:
BUSINESS AUTO COVERAGE FORM
GARAGE COVERAGE FORM
Section II - LIABILITY COVERAGE is changed by adding the following exclusions:
14. Delivery
“Bodily injury” or “property damage” arising out of the ownership, maintenance, or use of an “auto”
when used for delivery of any kind.
